content:
Colonel Natalia Humeniuk told how the Ukrainian soldiers successfully fight the means of radar struggle against drones of the Russian occupation army.

Natalia Humeniuk's relevant comments provided liveTelelorphoneThe only news in the morning of March 19, 2024.

Thus, when asked by the presenter, how many defense forces with the help of the HRS the enemy drones were able to plant, the spokeswoman said that even the opponent complains of his publications on social networks for the effective work of Ukrainians.

“In different areas of the front differently. But even the occupiers themselves note and complain of their publications that the work of the EWS on our part is extremely effective. Like classics: not every drone flew even to the middle of the Dnieper, ”Natalia Humeniuk said.

As reported by the Armyinform, for the last day of the Defense Force of UkraineReflected the attacks of the enemyin seven directions.
